column2: "/ci2 1 Whether she's real or not, Hitsugi being embarrassed about her swimsuit is just too precious! I want to take her home with me!"
"/ci2 1 Thanks for your help! Ooh, imagine if the real Hitsugi was here! I could have a Hitsugi on each arm! You have to come back to Earth!"

"Oh, I'm done for...
My Hitsugi harem plan ended before it even began..."
"No, my Hitsugi! You monsters! I'll never forgive you for this!"
